data.description:
Back on the market! BUYER COULD NOT PERFORM.
Welcome to this updated modern home! You'll be greeted by a captivating private courtyard, an idyllic spot for relaxation or entertaining. The cozy living/dining room is accentuated by wood plank tile floors with clean modern designs and recessed lighting, creating an inviting atmosphere for gathering. The kitchen boasts white cabinets, granite counters that extend throughout the entire home, and SS appliances, making meal preparation an enjoyable experience. Retreat to the main bedroom with a skylight, private access to the Bonus room, and on suite bathroom for added comfort. The 2nd bedroom offers direct access to the courtyard, making it an ideal space for guests or a home office. The backyard offers ample space for outdoor activities.
